descriptionHTML:
REQUIRES FACE FOR WEAR
======================

'til one is a return to classic, stylish faces and supports round or square faces. You must have Face for Wear installed and operational (the latest version is required) in order to use this face.

The first in a series of faces designed to be fashionable and beautiful, One is absolutely perfect for those nights out on a date, interview or professional meeting, or formal event.

* Supports Ambient Mode for always-on devices
* Simple, elegant design for a variety of outings

PLEASE NOTE: IF YOU ARE GETTING AN ERROR 4 UPON LOADING THE FACE YOUR FACE FOR WEAR APP IS LIKELY OUT OF DATE. DOWNLOAD THE LATEST UPDATE AND TRY TO SYNC AGAIN.
comments: Elegant watch face Very nice formal look.
